        "page_number": 2,
        "section_heading": "Page 2",
        "paragraph_or_text_span": "The Initial Management of Chronic Pelvic Pain This is the second edition of this guideline. The first edition was published in 2005 under the same title. 1. Purpose and scope The purpose of this guideline is to provide an evidence-based summary for the generalist to facilitate appropriate investigation and management of women presenting for the first time with chronic pelvic pain. 2. Background an",
